008 年，今年的冻雨天气是瞬时「速冻」 | 每经网"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-a03d94790ff0650876242995e02af456_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "热度累计中", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/643266306"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I8J6Sz/ejqdAKEAMaCTEwNTIyNTczMyC5nYiuBjAAOCtAInIJNjQzMjY2MzA2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "35_1707311273.617917", "card_id": "Q_642405036", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 109}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "有哪些除夕的封神古诗词？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-06c5053f5e3a7fcf5abfd35380399484_b.gif"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "热度累计中", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/642405036"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI8J6Sz/ejqdAKEAMaCTEwNTAzNDE3NSCLiu6tBjAAOL0CQCNyCTY0MjQwNTAzNngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "36_1707311273.618145", "card_id": "Q_642908119", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 74}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "连续骑行 100 公里和跑半马哪个更难？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-356d79180c31a9ec4a70cbd707bbc496_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "热度累计中", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/642908119"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I8J6Sz/ejqdAKEAMaCTEwNTE0NjAxNSDP1f2tBjAAOGRAJHIJNjQyOTA4MTE5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "37_1707311273.618352", "card_id": "Q_643270027", "feed_specific": {"answer_cou